<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About ExTodo</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --brand-dark: #2c3e50;
      --accent-color: #e74c3c;
      --background-color: #f5f7fa;
      --card-bg: #ffffff;
      --text-dark: #333333;
      --text-light: #6b7280;
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
                   0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      background: var(--background-color);
      color: var(--text-dark);
      padding-top: 80px;
      padding-bottom: 60px;
    }

    main {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-section {
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    h1 {
      color: var(--brand-dark);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('navbar') %>

  <main>
    <div class="about-section">
      <h1>About ExTodo</h1>
      <p>
        ExTodo is a powerful and intuitive to-do list application designed to help you stay organized and productive. 
        Whether you're managing personal tasks, work projects, or collaborative efforts, ExTodo provides the tools you need to keep track of everything that matters.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mission is to simplify task management and empower users to achieve their goals with ease. 
        This application is built with Node.js, Express, and EJS, offering a fast, reliable, and user-friendly experience.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('footer') %>
</body>
</html>